Hello all
in macros.css i am getting an error:- Minification failed due to JS parsing error <https://app.HubSpot.com/design-manager/3074142/code/62116552785?show_compiled_output=true|(Show output with ESLint enabled)>: `Unknown error`
i am not getting how to deal with this , below snippet is available in my macros.css
```{% set macros = true %}
{% macro color(value) %}

  {% set colorhex = value.color|convert_rgb %}
  {% if value.opacity != null %}
    {% set coloropacity = value.opacity / 100 %}
  {% else %}
    {% set coloropacity = '1' %}
  {% endif %}


  rgba({{ colorhex }}, {{ coloropacity }})

{% endmacro %}```
